text: Park Je-sun (; , 7 December 1858 – 20 June 1919) was a Korean politician and diplomat during the Joseon dynasty.Park Je-sun He was the Prime Minister of the Korean Empire between 1905 to 1907, and 1909 to 1910. He was a very important person of the Japan–Korea Treaty of 1910. == Other websites == * Park Je-sun * Park Je-sun == References == Category:1858 births Category:1919 deaths Category:Korean educators Category:Korean politicians
